337
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:01,690
Hej, ty hajzle, seš mrtvej?!

338
00:31:02,330 --> 00:31:05,820
Jestli seš mrtvej, tak to alespoň, ty kreténe!

339
00:31:31,330 --> 00:31:35,120
Koukej vylízt...

340
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:38,550
